Dec 5 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Friday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

HARGREAVES LANSDOWN PLC <HRGV.L> The British investment platform operator said Chief Financial Officer Tracey Taylor had decided to step down from the role with immediate effect. [ID:nL3N0TP3Z6]  KPMG [KPMG.UL] The audit and advisory firm said it hired in Switzerland a team of banking and sourcing experts from B-Source. [ID:nL3N0TP35F]  INTEGRO